videoDetails.Title: Choosing the Right War Thunder Ground Tech Tree in 2023
videoDetails.Description:
War Thunder has a total of 10 ground tech trees in the game in this War Thunder Video we will be going over what a new or returning player should pick when it comes to nations. This Video covers America, Germany, USSR(Russia), Britain, Japan, China, Italy, France, Sweden, and Israel. Hopefully this video will put you in the right direction for which tech tree you should grind in WarThunder.
